title: H.R. Pufnstuf, child of the '60s, visits Nickelodeon show
text: > Entertainment H.R. Pufnstuf, child of the '60s, visits Nickelodeon show This photo provided by Nickelodeon shows Calvin Millan, left, as Calvin, Stuff, and clockwise at top right, Zippy, Grandma, Giggles and Wiggles in season one of "Mutt & Stuff," on Nickelodeon. H.R. Pufnstuf, the title character of the 1969-71 children’s series will appear on an episode of Nickelodeon’s new preschool series “Mutt & Stuff,” the cable channel said Tuesday, Oct. 13, 2015.(Robert Voets/Nickelodeon via AP)
